                                        <foreign xml:lang="ja">Taishō</foreign>
                                    </hi> edition). Continuation of the text in cave <hi rend="bold">73</hi>, wall e, which ends with chapter 6 in scroll 2 of the <hi rend="italic">Golden Light Sutra</hi>.</cell>
                            </row>
                            <row>
                                <cell>Column 36:</cell>
                                <cell>
                                    <foreign xml:lang="zh">怚荼  陀也反 </foreign> and <foreign xml:lang="zh">他富樓抳  諾履反</foreign> (<foreign xml:lang="zh">陀也反</foreign> and <foreign xml:lang="zh">諾履反</foreign> in small characters, these being two notes on pronunciation towards the end of the column). </cell>
                            </row>
