                                <cell>Column 41:</cell>
                                <cell>
                                    <foreign xml:lang="zh">怨賊災横及諸毒害解除五</foreign>: the last eleven characters on this wall. The carved text ends here, abruptly, within the fourth <hi rend="italic">
                                        <foreign xml:lang="sa">dhāraṇī</foreign>
                                    </hi> in <hi rend="nh">chapter</hi> 7.
